  "title": "Widget & UI Scale System",
  "description": "Allows Players to Scale their Game UI from one Slider. Add Scaling UI to your existing Game/Widgets or create new ones, in seconds.",
  "longDescription": "<p>[ <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v&#61;Ui5kitNhUcY&amp;list&#61;PLYTJTwFgZh8I9FMExpb1kzAhv7ma7BRWL\" rel=\"nofollow\">Quick Showcase &amp; Tutorials</a> ] [ <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1omBKfw8sSZQf5mmd669-DF4uYpV6M0nZvHgvw7xGUzY/edit?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">Documentation </a>] [ <a href=\"https://discord.gg/F8sdjPvyV7\" rel=\"nofollow\">Support Discord</a> ]</p><p><strong>Game UI Scaling Made Easy!</strong></p><ul><li><em>Empower players to scale their UI with a single slider.</em></li></ul><p>With our Widget &amp; UI Scale System, players can seamlessly adjust the size of their in-game UI elements using just one intuitive slider, putting the power of customization right at their fingertips.</p><ul><li><em>Instantly integrate UI scaling into existing widgets or create new ones in seconds.</em></li></ul><p>What sets our toolkit apart is its remarkable versatility. Easily incorporate our Widget Blueprint Scaling Widget into your existing game widgets or create brand new ones, all within a matter of seconds. Whether you&#39;re a seasoned developer or just starting out, achieving UI scalability has never been more accessible.</p><ul><li><em>The global scale slider effortlessly integrates into any menu (widget).</em></li></ul><p>The real gem lies in the global scale slider, a game-changer in UI personalization. This slider can be effortlessly integrated into any menu widget, and it automatically scales all widgets that integrate our Widget Blueprint Scaling Widget, on Player demand.</p><ul><li><em>Scale Value auto-loads on startup , auto-saves on slider destruction, and auto-applies on widget creation</em></li></ul><p>To enhance the user experience further, we&#39;ve designed our system for seamless integration. It auto-loads on initialization, ensuring that your players get the perfect UI from the moment they launch the game. Plus, we&#39;ve streamlined the process by enabling auto-save functionality upon the slider&#39;s destruction, making customization effortlessly convenient.</p><p><br /></p><p><em>&#34;Create a more inclusive (eyesight) and enjoyable gaming journey (UI size preference) for your audience.&#34;</em></p><p><br /></p><p><em>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</em></p><p><strong>Features: </strong></p><p>1. Single Slider Control:</p><ul><li>Empower players to scale their UI with a single slider.</li><li>Seamlessly adjust the size of in-game UI elements with ease.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>2. Versatile Integration:</p><ul><li>Instantly integrate UI scaling into existing widgets or create new ones in seconds.</li><li>Incorporate our Widget Blueprint Scaling Widget effortlessly into your game widgets.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>3. Global Scale Slider:</p><ul><li>Effortless UI Personalization:The global scale slider integrates seamlessly into any menu widget.</li><li>Automatically scales all widgets integrated with our Widget Blueprint Scaling Widget on player demand.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>4. Automatic Handling:</p><ul><li>UI Scale Value Auto-Load:Auto-loads UI scale value on game startup for a perfect UI from the beginning.</li><li>Auto-Save Functionality:Auto-saves UI scale settings when the slider is removed, ensuring convenient customization.</li><li>Auto-Apply on Widget Creation:Automatically applies UI scale settings to newly created widgets.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>5. Enhanced User Experience:</p><ul><li>Create a more inclusive gaming experience by accommodating different eyesight and UI size preferences.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><em>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</em></p>",
